\id 1TI - Baibal Kathoung New Testament 
\h 1 TIMOTE 
\toc1 1 TIMOTE 
\toc2 1 Timote 
\toc3 1 Tim 
\mt1 1 TIMOTE  
\mt2 (The First Epistle of Paul to Timothy)  
\c 1  
\s1 Lawk karouknae  
\p
\v 1 Kai Pawl, na ka rungngangkung Cathut hoi, maimouh ni ngaihawi e Jisuh Khrih e kâpoelawk lahoi Jisuh Khrih e guncei lah kaawm e ni yuemnae lahoi ka ca katang lah kaawm e Timote koe ca na patawn.  
\v 2 Na pa Cathut hoi maimae Jisuh Khrih koehoi lungmanae, pahrennae hoi lungmawngnae teh nang koe awm lawiseh.   
\s1 Kâhruetcuet poenae  
\p
\v 3 Masidonia ram lah ka cei navah kai ni na hroecoe e patetlah Efisa kho la na o teh, alouklouk e cangkhainae cangkhai hoeh nahanelah,  
\v 4 lairuipakong hoi ka pout thai hoeh e miphun tâconae hah banglah pouk awh hoeh nahanelah, cingthui haw. Hote hnonaw niteh yuemnae hlak kâounnae doeh a tâco sak.  
\v 5 Hatei kâpoelawk ni ngainae teh, kathounge lungthin hoi thoseh, kathounge mahoima kâpanuenae hoi thoseh, kathounge yuemnae hoi thoseh, kâkuen e lungpatawnae hah doeh.  
\v 6 Hote hno dawk hoi tami tangawn ni a roun awh teh, aphu kaawm hoeh e lawk deinae koe lah a kamlang awh toe.  
\v 7 Bangpatetlae phung koe lah maw kacaklah ka o awh tie hai kâpanuek awh laipalah, kacangkhaikung saya lah o han a ngai awh bo aw.   
\p
\v 8 Kâlawk teh hnokahawi kasaknaw hanelah ta e nahoeh.  
\v 9 Kâlawklaipa hoi lawkkangaihoehnaw, cathutlaipa hoi tamikayonnaw, kathounghoehnaw hoi lawkkatang banglahai ka pouk hoeh e naw, manu kathetnaw hoi na pa kathetnaw,  
\v 10 tami kathetnaw, kamsoumhoehe napui tongpa yonnae kasaknaw, tongpa reira yonnae kasaknaw, tami kaparawtnaw, laithoe kadeinaw, laithoe koe lah thoekâbonaw, kathounge cangkhainae katarannaw pueng hanelah doeh kâlawk teh ta pouh e lah ao. Hote kâlawk hah hmantang ka hno e taminaw teh, hote kâlawk ni hawinae a poe.  
\v 11 Hottelah ka ti navah, Yawhawi Cathut e bawilen kamthang kahawi teh kai na poe toe.   
\s1 Pawl ni a kampangkhainae  
\p
\v 12 Kai hah thaonae hoi na kakawisakkung maimae Bawipa Khrih Jisuh e a lungmanae teh ka pholen. Bangkongtetpawiteh, ahni ni a thaw tawk hane lah na rawi teh yuemkamcu lah na pouk toe.  
\v 13 Kai teh ahmaloe vah, kapathoekung, kadudamkung, ayâ karektapkung lah ka o eiteh, yuemhoehnae hoi panuek laipalah hoi ka tawksak e a tho dawkvah, lungmanae ka coenae doeh.  
\v 14 Maimae Bawipa e a lungmanae haiyah, Khrih Jisuh thung kaawm e yuemnae hoi lungpatawnae hoi cungtalah pouk e hlak a kuep toe.   
\p
\v 15 Khrih Jisuh ni het talaivan a tho ngainae teh tamikayon rungngang hanlah a tho tie teh, yuemkamcu e hoi dâw hane roeroe lah a kamcu. Hote tamikayonnaw thung dawkvah kai teh kalenpounge lah ka o.  
\v 16 Hateiteh, a yungyoe hringnae coe nahanlah ka yuem hane naw ni a dawn han kawi lah ao nahan, kalenpounge yonnae ka tawn e kai hah Jisuh Khrih ni lungsawnae hoi panguepnae na patue toe.  
\v 17 A yungyoe siangpahrang, kangning e, hmuthaihoehe, Cathut buet touh dueng teh barinae, bawilennae a yungyoe hoi a yungyoe awm lawiseh, Amen.   
\p
\v 18 Ka capa Timote, nang hanelah profet lahoi ka pâpho e naw hoi hete cingthuilawknaw hah nang koe na poe. Hethateh, yuemnae hoi kathounge panuenae lung na tawn teh kahawi e tarankâtuknae na tuk thai nahane doeh.  
\v 19 Tami tangawn ni yuemnae a takhoe awh dawkvah, yuemnae long a rawk teh rawknae koe a pha awh toe.  
\v 20 Hotnaw thung dawkvah Himenaias hoi Alexander a bawk roi. Ahnimouh roi ni Cathut dudamnae lawk a dei roi hoeh nahanelah a kamtu roi nahan Setan kut dawk ka poe toe.   
\c 2  
\s1 Cathut bawknae  
\p
\v 1 Tami pueng hanelah hai thoseh, siangpahrangnaw hoi kâ katawnnaw hanelah hai thoseh,  
\v 2 ratoum pouh hane hoi lunghawilawkdeinae ahmaloe na sak awh nahan kai ni na hroecoe.  
\v 3 Hottelah tinae teh maimae rungngangkung Cathut hmalah ngai kaawm e lah doeh ao.  
\v 4 Tami pueng rungngang lah o vaiteh, lawkkatang panuenae koe pha sak hanelah Cathut ni a ngainae ao.  
\v 5 Cathut teh buet touh dueng doeh kaawm. Cathut hoi taminaw rahak tami lah kaawm e Khrih Jisuh buet touh dueng doeh laicei lah kaawm.  
\v 6 Ahni ni tami pueng ratang hanelah a tak a pasoung toe. A tue a pha toteh a kamnue sak.  
\v 7 Kai teh kapâphokung lah thoseh, guncei lah thoseh, yuemnae hoi Khrih thung e lawkkatang hah Jentelnaw koe ka pâpho hane saya lahai thoseh, na ta toe. Hottelah ka dei nah laithoe ka dei hoeh, hmantang doeh ka dei.   
\s1 Tongpanaw hoi napuinaw hanelah cingthuinae  
\p
\v 8 Tongpanaw ni hmuen tangkuem koe, lungkhueknae, kâounnae awm laipalah, kathounge kut dâw laihoi na ratoum awh nahanlah na ngaikhai awh.  
\v 9 Hot patetvanlah, napuinaw ni samveinae, sui, pale, aphu kaawm e khohnanaw hoi kamthoup laipalah, mitkhet kamcu lah kamthoup awh nateh, lungdo lungnem lahoi kacuemkamui lah awm awh.  
\v 10 Cathut ka barilawa e napuinaw ni a kamthoup hanelah ao e patetlah, kamcu e nuen hoi kamthoup awh na seh.   
\p
\v 11 Napuinaw teh lawkngai laihoi lawkkamuem lah kamtu naseh.  
\v 12 Napui teh tongpanaw lathueng cangkhainae hoi kâtawnnae ka poe hoeh. Napui teh lawkkamuem ao hanlah ao.  
\v 13 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Adam hmaloe a sak hnukkhu Evi sak e lah ao.  
\v 14 Hothloilah, Adam teh tacuek lah awm hoeh, Evi doeh tacuek lah kaawm niteh ka payon.  
\v 15 Hateiteh, napuinaw teh, kacuemkamui lah onae, yuemnae, lungpatawnae, thoungnae dawk awm awh pawiteh, cakhenae dawk rungngang lah ao awh han.   
\c 3  
\s1 Bishop lah kuepnae  
\p
\v 1 Tami buet touh ni bishop thaw tawk hanelah ngai pawiteh thaw kahawi ka ngai e lah ao.  
\v 2 Bishopnaw teh, tounhoehe, napui buet touh e vâ lah kaawm e,, kâhruetcuet e, kacuemkamui lah kaawm e, imyin ka ngai e, ka cangkhai thai e han.  
\v 3 Yamuhri lah kaawm hoeh e, ka pahngawpahrak hoeh e, kamsoum hoeh lahoi tangka hmu ka ngai hoeh e, a lung kanem e, ayâ hoi kâyue hoeh e, tangka ka hounloun hoeh e han.  
\v 4 Ama e imthung kahawicalah ka uk thai niteh, a canaw ka yue ka toun thai e tami han.  
\v 5 Ama e imthungkhu patenghai kahawicalah hrawi thai hoehpawiteh bangtelamaw kawhmoun a khetyawt thai han.  
\v 6 Kâthungtahma e tami mahoeh. Telah nahoeh pawiteh, ahni ni kâoup vaiteh, kahraimathout hoi kâvan e yonphukhangnae dawk bawt payon vaih tie ngaihrinae ao.  
\v 7 Pathoenae awm laipalah kahraimathout mannae dawk hoi a hlout nahan, alawilae taminaw koe bari kaawm e tami han.   
\s1 hotunaw  
\p
\v 8 Hot patetvanlah, hotunaw hai a lung kacakpounge han. A lai ka samphei e, yamuhri lah kaawm e tami mahoeh. Kathounghoehe tangka hmunae ka ngai hoeh e tami han.  
\v 9 Ma hoi ma kâpanuenae lung a thoung vaiteh yuemnae a dungkawnae hah mangkhak kangdoutkhai e tami han.  
\v 10 Ahnimouh hai tanouknae hmaloe a kâhmo awh hnukkhu, tounhoehe lah awm pawiteh, hotunaw thaw tawk awh naseh.   
\p
\v 11 Ahnimae yunaw hai a lung kacakpounge lah ao awh han. Tamcueklawk ka dei e lah awm laipalah, kâhruetcuet e, lawkkam kacakpounge lah ao awh han.   
\p
\v 12 Hotunaw teh, napui buet touh e vâ lah ao han. A yu a ca kahawicalah ka uk thai e han.  
\v 13 Bangkongtetpawiteh, hotunaw thaw kahawicalah katawknaw teh, amamouh hanelah min hawinae a hmu awh hloilah, Khrih Jisuh thung yuemnae dawkvah, taranhawinae a hmu awh.   
\s1 Cathut lawk dawk hringnae  
\p
\v 14 Nang koe ca ka thut ngainae teh nang koe karanglah ka tho hane ka ngaihawi ei,  
\v 15 ka hnawng pawiteh Cathut e imthung dawkvah bangtelamaw kâroekâkhawi han tie hah, na panue thai nahanlah, hettelah ka thut teh na patawn. Hote im hateh, kahring Cathut e Kawhmoun doeh, lawkkatang e khom hoi adu pui doeh.  
\v 16 Cathut lawk hoi khosaknae teh atangcalah adungkaw tangngak. Cathut teh takthai dawk a kamnue toe. Muitha lahoi a katang doeh titeh a kampangkhai. Kalvantaminaw nihai a hmu awh toe. Jentelnaw nihai kamthang lawk a thai awh toe. Talaivan taminaw nihai a yuem awh toe. Bawilennae hoi lathueng lah tawm lah ao toe.   
\c 4  
\s1 Kamsoumhoehe kacangkhaikungnaw  
\p
\v 1 Muitha ni kamcengcalah a pâpho e teh, a to hmalah teh dumyennae muithanaw hoi kahraituilinaw e cangkhainae dawkvah dawn awh vaiteh, yuemnae a ceitakhai awh han.  
\v 2 Hote cangkhai e naw teh, amamae panuenae lung hah sumhmaisaan hoi kânep awh niteh, a lai kathout e, tami kahawi lah ka kâsak e naw koehoi doeh a tho.  
\v 3 Ahnimouh ni kâpaluennae cakâ awh vaiteh, kayuem niteh lawkkatang ka panuek e taminaw ni lunghawilawkdeinae lahoi canei hane rawca Cathut ni a sak e hah a hai sak awh han.  
\v 4 Cathut ni a sak e pueng teh ahawi dawkvah lunghawilawkdeinae lahoi hno pawiteh, hnoun hane banghai awm hoeh.  
\v 5 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut e lawk lahoi thoseh, ratoum e lahoi thoseh, bangpueng teh a thoung.   
\s1 Jisuh e san kahawi  
\p
\v 6 Hete lawknaw hah hmaunawnghanaw koe na dei pouh pawiteh, Jisuh Khrih e thaw ka tawk e, yuemnae lawknaw hoi kawkhik e lah na o han.  
\v 7 Napui matawngnaw ni ouk a dei awh e lairuipakongnaw hah takhoe nateh, Cathutlae khosaknae lahoi namahoima kâcangkhai haw.  
\v 8 Takthai dawk kâ cangkhainae teh hawinae moikapap awmhoeh. Cathut lawk dawk khosaknae teh atu e hringnae hoi due hnukkhu e hringnae totouh lawkkamnae ao dawkvah, bangpueng hanelah hawinae ao.  
\v 9 Hethateh yuemkamcu e hoi dâw hane roeroe lah kamcu e doeh.  
\v 10 Hatdawkvah, maimouh teh hot hanelah thapatho teh panki laihoi tawk awh. Bangkongtetpawiteh, tami pueng rungngangkung, alawkpui lah kayuemnaw e rungngangkung lah kaawm e kahring Cathut hah maimouh ni ngaihawi awh.   
\s1 A thawtawknae dawk lamthung pâtuenae  
\p
\v 11 Hete hnonaw hah kâ poe nateh cangkhaih.  
\v 12 Na nawnae hah apinihai, dudam hanh naseh. Lawk deinae, kâroekâkhawinae, ayânaw lungpatawnae, muitha hoi hringnae, lawkkamcaknae, thoungnae dawkvah, kayuemnaw han khetsin hanelah awm loe.  
\v 13 Kai ka tho hoehroukrak Cakathoung touknae, thapoenae hoi cangkhainae hah panki laihoi pou sak loe.  
\v 14 Kacuenaw e kut toung e hoi sutdeilawk lahoi, nang koe poe lah kaawm e poehno hah noutna laipalah awm hanh.  
\v 15 Na roungnae teh taminaw koe kamnue sak nahanelah, hotnaw hah panki loe.  
\v 16 Nama hoi nama na kâcangkhai nakunghai thoseh, na cangkhai e dawk hai thoseh, kâhruetcuet nateh pou awm loe. Hottelah na tetpawiteh nama hoi na lawk kathainaw hah na rungngang han.   
\c 5  
\s1 Kawhmoun Thung e Thaw  
\p
\v 1 Tongpa matawngnaw hah puenghoi yue laipalah, na pa patetlah thapoe loe. Tongpa kanaw hah hmaunawngha patetlah pouk loe.  
\v 2 Napui matawngnaw hah na manu patetlah pouk nateh, tanglanaw hah kathoungpounge na tawncei patetlah pouk loe.   
\p
\v 3 Lahmai lah kaawm katang e napuinaw hah bari nateh khenyawn loe.  
\v 4 Hateiteh, hote lahmainu ni a ca catounnaw tawn pawiteh, hote ca catounnaw ni Cathut thaw lah a pouk awh vaiteh, mae im a khetyawt hoi, manu na pa mintoenaw khetyawtnae kamtu awh naseh. Hottelah tawknae teh Cathut ni a ngai e doeh.  
\v 5 Khenyawnkung awm laipalah amadueng kaawm e lahmainu teh, Cathut kâuep laihoi karum khodai pout laipalah ouk a ratoum.  
\v 6 Hatei, talai van nawmnae dawk ka cet e lahmainu teh a hring nahlangva kadout e lah ao.  
\v 7 Apinihai tounhoehe lah ao nahan kâ poe loe.  
\v 8 Apipatethai imthung ka khenyawn hoeh e teh yuemnae ka pahnawt e lah ao teh, kayuemhoehnaw hlak hoe a mathoe.   
\p
\v 9 Kum 60 kakuep hoeh rae teh lahmainu lah khoe hanh loe, a vâ buet touh dueng ouk kaawm e,  
\v 10 a canaw kahawicalah ka khen thai e, imyin ka ngai e, tami kathoungnaw e khok ka pâsu e, rucat ka kâhmo e naw ka khenyawn e, kahawi hno kaawm e pueng ka tawk e lah awm pawiteh, lahmai lah khoe han.   
\p
\v 11 A kum kanaw e lahmainunaw teh, lahmainu lah khoe hanh loe. Bangkongtetpawiteh, Khrih e cangkhainae ngâi hoeh, vâ sak hanelah ngai pawiteh,  
\v 12 ahmaloe lawkkam a raphoe dawkvah, yonphukhangnae ao han.  
\v 13 Im touh hnukkhu im touh a luen awh teh, a pangak awh. Hottelah a pangak awh dueng tho laipalah, tamthoe a dei awh teh ayânaw e lai dawk a kâphum awh teh, dei kawi hoeh e hah ouk a dei awh.  
\v 14 Hatdawkvah, kanaw e lahmainu teh a vâ bout a tawn vaiteh, a canaw bout sak naseh. Ayâ ni bout pathoe hoeh nahanlah a imthung kahawicalah bout tawn naseh, pathoenae heh taran ni a tha kâla hoeh nahan lah.  
\v 15 Lahmainu tangawn teh, lam a payon awh teh setan hnuk a kâbang awh toe.   
\p
\v 16 Ka yuem e napui hoehpawiteh, tongpa ni ama hoi kâkuen e lahmainu tawn pawiteh, khenyawn naseh. Hat pawiteh doeh, lahmainu katangnaw hah tarawknae awm laipalah, kawhmoun ni a khetyawt thai han.   
\p
\v 17 Kahawicalah ka uk e kacuenaw, alawkpui lah lawk pâphonae hoi cangkhainae dawkvah, panki laihoi ka tawk e kahrawikungnaw teh, let hni touh barinae lah awm awh naseh.  
\v 18 Cakathoung ni cangkatin lahun e maitotan a pahni moum pouh hanh, thawtawkkung ni a tawknae phu hmu hanelah a kamcu, telah bout a ti.  
\v 19 Kacue ni hno a sakpayon nah, kapanuekkhaikung kahni kathum touh awmhoeh pawiteh hote yonpennae teh dâw pouh hanh loe.  
\v 20 Alouke taminaw ni a taki nahan yonnae ka sak e tami teh taminaw hmalah yue loe.   
\p
\v 21 Kapeknae tawn laipalah, bang patet e hno dawk hai, kâkangkhai e tawn laipalah na tawk nahan, Bawipa Jisuh Khrih hoi Cathut hmalah, rawi lah kaawm e kalvantami hmalah ka patawpoung lah na hroecoe.   
\p
\v 22 Apipatet e lathueng haiyah, kuttoungnae hmatara sak pouh hanh loe. Ayâ alouknaw e lumlai dawk hai bawk hanh loe. Nama hoi nama kamthoung loe.   
\p
\v 23 Na vonpui patawnae hoi atuhoitu na damhoehnae dawkvah, tui dueng net laipalah misurtui hai youn touh net khai loe.   
\p
\v 24 Tami tangawn e yon teh lawkceng hoehnahlan a kamphawng toe. A tangawn e yon teh a hnukkhu doeh ouk a kamphawng.  
\v 25 Hot patetvanlah hnokahawi sak e haiyah, bangpatet teh tang a kamnue, kamnuek hoeh rae hnokahawi sak e hai hrawk thai mahoeh.   
\c 6  
\s1 Bawi barilawanae  
\p
\v 1 Cathut min hoi cangkhainae teh dudam e lah ao hoeh nahan, patoun e san niteh a bawipa hah a bari hanelah a kamcu tie panuek naseh.  
\v 2 A bawipa teh ka yuem e lah awm pawiteh, hmaunawngha doeh tie lung hoi hnephnap laipalah, hoe kahawicalah tawk pouh awh naseh. Bangkongtetpawiteh, kahawicalah tawk pouh e ka coe e bawi teh, ka yuem e tami, lungpataw kawi e tami lahai ao. Hetnaw heh cangkhai nateh hroecoe loe.   
\s1 Alouke cangkhainae hoi hounlounnae  
\p
\v 3 Tami buetbuet touh ni ka thuem hoeh e cangkhainae hah a cangkhaia teh, maimae Bawipa Jesuh Khrih e kathounge cangkhainae hoi cathutlae cangkhainae ka tarawi hoeh e tami teh, lunglenpansa lah kaawm niteh banghai ka panuek hoeh e doeh.  
\v 4 Lawklung kâounnae hoi kamcan dawk a lung kapen e lah ao awh. Hot kecu dawkvah, hounroenae, kâyuenae, dudam lawk deinae, lunghringnae ouk a tâco.  
\v 5 Hottelah panuenae lung a kamko dawkvah, lawkkatang ka bawk hoeh e kâounnae lah ao teh, Cathut lawk dawk khosaknae teh aphu ao toungloung katetnaw koe ka pout thai hoeh e kâounnae ouk a tâcokhai.   
\p
\v 6 Hatei, lungkuepnae lahoi Cathut lawk dawk khosaknae teh aphu ao tangngak doeh.  
\v 7 Bangkongtetpawiteh, maimouh teh het talaivan dawk banghai sin laipalah tho awh dawkvah, banghai sin laipalah bout tâco awh han tie teh a kamceng.  
\v 8 Hatdawkvah, canei khohna han tawn e ca dawk lungkuep awh sei .  
\v 9 Tawnta han ka ngai e taminaw teh dumyennae dawk thoseh, karap dawk thoseh, taminaw kamkonae dawk ka bawt sak e radueknae dawk thoseh, ouk a bo awh.  
\v 10 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tangka lungpatawnae teh kahawihoehe hno pueng e a kung lah ao. Taminaw teh tangka thouk a hounloun awh dawkvah, yuemnae dawk hoi lam a phen awh teh, lungreithainae hoi runae a kâpoe awh.   
\s1 Yuemnae hoi kâkuen e kâtuknae  
\p
\v 11 Hatdawkvah, Oe! Cathut e tami, nang teh hote yonnae hah roun loe. Lannae, Cathut lawk dawk khosaknae, yuemnae, lungpatawnae, panguepnae, lungdo lungnemnae hah pou pâlei haw.  
\v 12 Yuemnae hoi kâkuen e, kahawi e kâtuknae hah tuk nateh, a yungyoe hringnae hah kuen nateh tawn loe. Nang teh hote hringnae hanlah, kaw lah na o dawkvah, kapanuekkhaikungnaw e hmalah kahawicalah na pâpho toe.  
\v 13 Khrih Jisuh a kamnue ditouh, nang teh tounhoehe lah na o nahanlah, kaie kâpoelawk na tarawi nahan,  
\v 14 a cawngca pueng kahring sak e Cathut hmalah hai thoseh, Pontius Pailat bawi hmalah hai thoseh, kahawicalah pâphonae lahoi kampangkhai e Bawipa Jisuh Khrih hmalah hai thoseh, kai ni kâ na poe.  
\v 15 A tue a kuep toteh Cathut ni Khrih a kamnue sak han. Cathut teh yawhawinae ao teh, buet touh dueng e ukkung Bawi lah ao. Siangpahrang pueng e Siangpahrang, bawi pueng e Bawi lah ao.  
\v 16 Bawipa dueng doeh duenae dawk hoi kahlout niteh, rek hnai thai hoeh e angnae dawk kaawm. Taminaw thung dawk api buet touh nihai Cathut teh hmawt awh boihoeh, hmawt hai hmawt thai awh hoeh. Hote Cathut teh bahu hoi barinae a yungyoe awm lawiseh. Amen.   
\s1 Katawntanaw kâhruetcuet poenae  
\p
\v 17 Atu e hringnae dawk tangka katawntanaw teh, kâoupnae lung tawn laipalah, kangning hoeh e hnopai kâuep laipalah, maimouh ni coe hane ka kuep lah na ka poe e kahring Cathut kâuep nahanlah cingthui loe.  
\v 18 Ayânaw hanlah hnokahawi saknae, nuencang kahawi hoi kamsi laipalah ka poe e naw lah coungkacoe ao awh nahan,  
\v 19 hringnae katang a coe awh nahanelah due hnukkhu hringnae adu a ung thai awh nahanlah cingthui loe.   
\p
\v 20 Oe! Timote, nang koe na poe e naw hah tarawi loe, Cathut lawk hoi kâkuen hoeh e ayawmyin lah dei e lawknaw hoi, talai thoumthainae lahoi kâtaran lah deinae hah roun loe.  
\v 21 Hote talai thoumnae hah, tami tangawn ni kampangkhai e lahoi, yuemnae lamthung a phen awh toe. Nang koe lungmanae awm lawiseh. Amen.   